file.name: types.yml
file.content:
---
openapi: "3.0.1"
paths:
  /simple.TypesService/DoSomething:
    post:
      summary: "Do Something"
      operationId: "simple.TypesService.DoSomething"
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/simple.TypesInput"
          application/protobuf:
            schema:
              type: "object"
      responses:
        200:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/simple.TypesOutput"
            application/protobuf:
              schema:
                type: "object"
components:
  schemas:
    simple.TypesInput:
      type: "object"
      properties:
        float_field:
          type: "number"
          format: "float"
        int64_field:
          type: "string"
          format: "int64"
        fixed64_field:
          type: "string"
          format: "fixed64"
        int32_field:
          type: "number"
          format: "int32"
        fixed32_field:
          type: "number"
          format: "fixed32"
        uint32_field:
          type: "number"
          format: "uint32"
        double_field:
          type: "number"
          format: "double"
        uint64_field:
          type: "string"
          format: "uint64"
    simple.TypesOutput:
      type: "object"
